      "span_text": "Analyses were piecemeal, mostly descriptive, and only 144 children of the whole set were investigated for anthropometric, radiographic and cognitive relationships. [CITATION_1] Paper records have been converted to electronic files for all anthropometric and cognitive data, as well as for hand-wrist radiographs of all Maya and as many ladino and European children as possible within budgetary and time constraints.",
